::Kluster::

Kluster grins at Phobia.

"Don't forget, you're a Predacon too," he says, then turning serious, "But 
flying this ship against the Iron Fist would not be a good idea, either. It 
was designed for space travel, to send down shuttles for landings. Its 
manuverability might be greater than the Iron Fists, but we'll still have 
problems. A normal attack might be better."
